      "content": "hey, i'm working on a script for a gritty crime thriller set in a big city. i need help writing a really intense description of a neighborhood that's basically falling apart—the kind of place where you feel like you have to watch your back the second you step off the bus. can you give me some vivid, sensory details that show the social decay and the tension in the air? setting the mood is super important.",
