      "content": "that's a great start, really sets the vibe. to push it even further, i want to start introducing some characters that help establish why this place feels so dangerous. can you describe some of the people the protagonist might encounter walking down these streets at night? like, the types of people who actually live there or hang out on the corners—what are they wearing, what are they doing, and what kind of energy do they give off that makes someone feel unsafe?",
